OL,3,CPolice officer charged after allegedly
OL,4,Clying to get out of speeding fine
OL,6,FA West Yorkshire Police officer, that
OL,7,Fis alleged to have provided a false or
OL,8,Fmisleading account to avoid a speeding
OL,9,Ffine, has been charged.
OL,11,FPC Abigail Byrne is due to appear in
OL,12,Fcourt next week charged with
OL,13,Fconspiracy to pervert the course of
OL,14,Fjustice, following an Independent
OL,15,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC)
OL,16,Fdirected investigation.
OL,18,FThe 29-year-old officer will appear at
OL,19,FBradford Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,20,F13 April.
