OL,3,CPolice officer charged after allegedly
OL,4,Clying to get out of speeding fine
OL,6,FThe charge relates to speeding
OL,7,Foffences in the Kirklees area in
OL,8,FJanuary 2025 and an allegation that PC
OL,9,FByrne provided a false or misleading
OL,10,Faccount to avoid receiving a sanction
OL,11,Ffor a speeding offence.
OL,13,FPC Byrne has been suspended from the
OL,14,FWest Yorkshire Police since September
OL,15,F2025.
